`meta
 `: title

    plumb lsp playground

Use this file with `[plumb lsp] attached. The final diagnostics section contains
intentional semantic errors; the entire file remains syntactically valid.

`#{#symbols} Document symbols

This heading, its explicit anchor, and the task below should appear in the
document symbol tree.

`## Nested symbol

This heading should be nested below `[Document symbols].

`-{.task #symbol-task} Task symbol nested in this section

`#{#navigation} Definition, hover, and references

Try go-to-definition, hover, find references, and rename on these links:

`- Same-file anchor: `->[Document symbols]{to="#symbols"}
`- Same-file explicit anchor: `->[local anchor]{to="#local-anchor"}
`- Cross-file anchor: `->[Exporter conclusion]{to="plumb-export.plumb#export-target"}
`- Cross-file document: `->[Notes playground]{to="plumb-notes.plumb"}
`- Repeated reference: `->[Exporter conclusion]{to="plumb-export.plumb#export-target"}
`- External autolink hover: `[https://example.test/a%20b]{.->}
`- Relative document Autolink: `[plumb-export.plumb#export-target]{.->}
`- Relative file Autolink: `[static/plumb-pipeline.svg]{.->}
`- Image file hover and definition: `img[pipeline]{src="static/plumb-pipeline.svg"}

`anchor{#local-anchor} Rename this id to update its references.

`#{#completion} Completion

Try completion after each relevant introducer in a temporary edit:

`- Type a single backtick at line start to choose Task with `[created], Autolink, or Link.
`- Type a single backtick in ordinary inline content to choose Autolink or Link.
`- Start a link label with ``->[ and select a document title.
`- Complete a path in ``->[target]{to="plumb-.
`- Complete a fragment in ``->[target]{to="plumb-export.plumb#.
`- Complete a same-file fragment in ``->[target]{to="#.
`- Complete an Autolink document path inside ``[plumb-]{.->}.
`- Complete a raw fragment inside ``[plumb-export.plumb#]{.->}.
`- Complete an image path in ``img[alt]{src="static/}.

`#{#rename} Rename

Rename the `[plumb-export.plumb] path in
`->[this link]{to="plumb-export.plumb"}. Rename `[local-anchor] from either
its declaration or this `->[reference]{to="#local-anchor"}.

`#{#actions} Code actions and task hover

Open `->[metadata-scratch.plumb]{to="metadata-scratch.plumb"} to try
`[Insert document metadata].

Place the cursor in this ordinary item and request `[Convert to task]：

`- Convert this item and add its created timestamp

Place the cursor in this task and request `[Add task created timestamp]：

`-{.task #missing-created} Add the missing created field

Place the cursor in this task and request Complete or Cancel. Hover shows its
state, id, and timestamps:

`-{
   .task #action-task created="2026-07-20T09:00:00+08:00" due="2026-07-30T17:00:00+08:00"
  } Close this task from a code action

This task is blocked while its dependency remains open, so Complete is omitted
but Cancel remains available:

`-{.task #open-dependency} Finish this dependency first
`-{.task #blocked-action depends="#open-dependency"} Try actions on a blocked task

Completing this recurring task closes the current instance and appends the next
instance with an advanced due date and a `[prev] reference:

`-{.task #recurring-action due="2026-07-27T17:00:00+08:00" recur=P1W} Advance this recurring task

`#{#export-target} Export target

The exporter playground links to this explicit anchor.

`# Intentional diagnostics

The following valid syntax deliberately produces semantic diagnostics:

`- Missing same-file anchor: `->[missing]{to="#missing-anchor"}
`- Missing file: `->[missing file]{to="missing-target.plumb"}
`- Missing cross-file anchor: `->[missing heading]{to="plumb-export.plumb#missing-anchor"}

`anchor{#duplicate-anchor} First duplicate target.
`anchor{#duplicate-anchor} Second duplicate target.

`-{
   .task #conflicted-task done="2026-07-20T09:00:00+08:00" canceled="2026-07-20T10:00:00+08:00"
  } Conflicting closed state
`-{.task #self-dependent depends="#self-dependent"} Self dependency

`note{.task} Invalid task owner

`span[not raw]{.$} Invalid math owner

`span[not verbatim]{.->} Invalid autolink owner

`[bad path.plumb]{.->} Invalid autolink target

`img[missing source]

`img[invalid source]{src="bad path.png"}

`img[unresolved image]{src="static/missing.png"}
